data.description: Looking for a beautiful home with lots of extras...here it is. Offering to PAINT TRIM WHITE PRIOR TO CLOSE. Plus as you enter the home you will see the two-story foyer with a sitting room and dining area with trey ceiling. What a way to impress with your visitors with a first view of your home. Downstairs has a small room just inside the hallway from the garage that would make a great office or exercise room. The kitchen is open to the family room for ease of entertaining and enjoying your family and guest. The kitchen has lots of cabinets, granite countertops and a center island perfect for that buffet/serving area. Room to back of home has been finished to enjoy as a sunroom or tv sports room, complete with window a/c so you can stay cool on the hot summer days. Upstairs you will find a large master bedroom and bath, plus three additional bedrooms. The master bath has separate tub and shower, double sinks and walk-in closet. The laundry room is also upstairs. One of the many great features of this home is the three-car garage with lots of cabinets and storage, pull down attic stairs with flooring in attic for additional storage. Both attics have attic fans. Lots of room for a workshop or that extra car. And take special notice of the gorgeous driveway and back patio areas. The front porch is a wonderful feature, large enough for seating area to sit and enjoy the beautiful mornings or afternoons. There is a building out back for all your lawn and garden tools and a fenced yard for the kiddos or pets. Did I mention the beautiful land scaping? Take note...this home has fabulous curb appeal, from the grass, the flowers, the trees, and even the rock area in the back yard, all to make this home stand out from the competition. NEW ROOF 2021 .New hot water heater, 2022. Make your appointment today before it's gone.
